Package org.apache.calcite.sql.type

Interface SqlOperandMetadata

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SqlOperandTypeChecker
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    OperandMetadataImpl, SqlWindowTableFunction.AbstractOperandMetadata
    public interface SqlOperandMetadata
extends SqlOperandTypeChecker
    Extension to SqlOperandTypeChecker that also provides names and types of particular operands.

    It is intended for user-defined functions (UDFs), and therefore the number of parameters is fixed.

    See Also:
